    All About Me

    I love meeting people from all over the world, and I make it my mission to provide memorable tours and experiences for my clients. I decided to become a professional Tourist+Guide in 2000 and haven’t stopped travelling since!

    When I’m not busy guiding, I spend time researching and exploring new options to help keep my tours fresh, interesting and relevant - which means returning clients will discover something new every time they tour with me. Take a look at what I offer and get in touch if you would like to work with me. I can’t wait to show you the world as I see it.
